South African multidisciplinary engineering firm GIBB has appointed Nana Magomola chairperson. She succeeds the late Dr Don Mkhwanazi. &nbsp; Magomola was the former director-general in the Office of the Premier of the North West provincial government. She has also been chairperson of Limpopo Tourism, MX Health, Transnet National Ports Authority tender board and the Petronet tender board.&nbsp;